{
  "$schema": "https://github.com/Microsoft/Application-Insights-Workbooks/blob/master/schema/workbook.json",
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "# SRE Agent スレッド別 日次コスト (USD)\n\nこの Workbook は SRE Agent の **スレッド単位の Azure Agent Unit (AAU) 使用量** を取得し、**AAU 単価 (USD / AAU)** を掛けて **日ごとのコスト** を可視化します。\n\n- 既定単価: **1 AAU = $0.10** (Azure 料金ページ記載)\n- 対象期間: **当月の 1 日 〜 本日** (基となる API が当月分のみを返すため、開始日・終了日は自動で固定されます)\n- `threadId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000` の行は、ユーザー スレッドに紐付かない集約コスト (日次レポート / 評価など) を示します。\n\n下の **サブスクリプション / リソース グループ / エージェント / API バージョン / AAU 単価** を選択してください。"
      },
      "name": "text - intro"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "style": "above",
        "queryType": 1,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "value::all"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "8f6a2c40-2c1f-49e0-9d1a-5b1c5c0a0a01",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "SubscriptionId",
            "label": "サブスクリプション",
            "type": 2,
            "isRequired": true,
            "query": "resourcecontainers\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.resources/subscriptions'\n| project value=subscriptionId, label=name\n| order by label asc\n| extend selected=row_number()==1",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "value::all"
            ],
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [],
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "timeContext": {
              "durationMs": 86400000
            },
            "queryType": 1,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
          },
          {
            "id": "8f6a2c40-2c1f-49e0-9d1a-5b1c5c0a0a02",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "ResourceGroup",
            "label": "リソース グループ",
            "type": 2,
            "isRequired": true,
            "query": "resources\n| where subscriptionId == '{SubscriptionId}'\n| summarize by resourceGroup\n| order by tolower(resourceGroup) asc\n| extend selected=row_number()==1\n| project value=resourceGroup, label=resourceGroup, selected",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "value::all"
            ],
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [],
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "timeContext": {
              "durationMs": 86400000
            },
            "queryType": 1,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
          },
          {
            "id": "8f6a2c40-2c1f-49e0-9d1a-5b1c5c0a0a03",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "AgentName",
            "label": "エージェント名",
            "type": 2,
            "isRequired": true,
            "query": "resources\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.app/agents'\n| where subscriptionId == '{SubscriptionId}'\n| where resourceGroup == '{ResourceGroup}'\n| project value=name, label=name\n| order by label asc\n| extend selected=row_number()==1",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "value::all"
            ],
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [],
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "timeContext": {
              "durationMs": 86400000
            },
            "queryType": 1,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
          },
          {
            "id": "8f6a2c40-2c1f-49e0-9d1a-5b1c5c0a0a04",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "ApiVersion",
            "label": "API バージョン",
            "type": 1,
            "isRequired": true,
            "value": "2025-05-01-preview"
          },
          {
            "id": "8f6a2c40-2c1f-49e0-9d1a-5b1c5c0a0a05",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "UnitPriceUsdPerAAU",
            "label": "AAU 単価 (USD / AAU)",
            "type": 1,
            "isRequired": true,
            "value": "0.10"
          },
          {
            "id": "8f6a2c40-2c1f-49e0-9d1a-5b1c5c0a0a06",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "StartDate",
            "label": "開始日 (当月 1 日, 自動)",
            "type": 1,
            "isRequired": true,
            "isHiddenWhenLocked": true,
            "query": "resourcecontainers\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.resources/subscriptions'\n| take 1\n| project value = format_datetime(startofmonth(now()), 'yyyy-MM-dd')",
            "queryType": 1,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "value::all"
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "8f6a2c40-2c1f-49e0-9d1a-5b1c5c0a0a07",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "EndDate",
            "label": "終了日 (本日, 自動)",
            "type": 1,
            "isRequired": true,
            "isHiddenWhenLocked": true,
            "query": "resourcecontainers\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.resources/subscriptions'\n| take 1\n| project value = format_datetime(now(), 'yyyy-MM-dd')",
            "queryType": 1,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "value::all"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "name": "parameters - 0"
    },
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "**選択中**: `{SubscriptionId}` / `{ResourceGroup}` / `{AgentName}`\n\n- API バージョン: **{ApiVersion}**\n- AAU 単価: **${UnitPriceUsdPerAAU} / AAU**\n- 対象期間 (自動): **{StartDate}** 〜 **{EndDate}**\n\n> `costUsd = aau × {UnitPriceUsdPerAAU}` で各行のコストを算出します。"
      },
      "name": "text - selected"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "title": "dailyUsageDetails (per-thread テーブル)",
        "queryType": 12,
        "size": 0,
        "showExportToExcel": true,
        "visualization": "table",
        "query": "{\"version\":\"ARMEndpoint/1.0\",\"data\":null,\"headers\":[],\"method\":\"GET\",\"path\":\"/subscriptions/{SubscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{ResourceGroup}/providers/Microsoft.App/agents/{AgentName}/dailyUsageDetails\",\"urlParams\":[{\"key\":\"startTime\",\"value\":\"{StartDate}\"},{\"key\":\"endTime\",\"value\":\"{EndDate}\"},{\"key\":\"api-version\",\"value\":\"{ApiVersion}\"}],\"batchDisabled\":true,\"transformers\":[{\"type\":\"jsonpath\",\"settings\":{\"tablePath\":\"$.value[*]\",\"columns\":[{\"path\":\"$.date\",\"columnid\":\"date\",\"columnType\":\"datetime\"},{\"path\":\"$.threadId\",\"columnid\":\"threadId\",\"columnType\":\"string\"},{\"path\":\"$.source\",\"columnid\":\"source\",\"columnType\":\"string\"},{\"path\":\"$.value\",\"columnid\":\"aau\",\"columnType\":\"double\"},{\"path\":\"$.name.value\",\"columnid\":\"metricName\",\"columnType\":\"string\"}]}}]}",
        "gridSettings": {
